properties.areaDesc: Foothills of the Northern Blue Mountains of Oregon; Foothills of the Blue Mountains of Washington
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 4 at 8:25AM PST until January 4 at 4:00PM PST by NWS Pendleton OR
properties.description:
* WHAT...West to Southwest winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50
mph.

* WHERE...In Washington, Foothills of the Blue Mountains of
Washington. In Oregon, Foothills of the Northern Blue
Mountains of Oregon.

* WHEN...Until 4 PM PST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM PST THIS AFTERNOON
